            . I am a Policeman. I was on duty, and saw the prisoner going down Wentworth-street, about two or three hundred yards from the coach-stand, carrying this coat; I asked him where he got it - he said a man had given him 2d. to carry it down the street; I asked him what man, and he said he did not know where to find him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
